04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "87d910d1-81e6-6b2a-cf35-99f37fd48078"], "h93bfbba2g8238g4c36ga814gd4e057df41f2": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "87d910d1-81e6-6b2a-cf35-99f37fd48078"], "hdc5d0db3g1c76g48b6ga4cag147d717fa4a3": ["| We are in agreement: A. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "87d910d1-81e6-6b2a-cf35-99f37fd48078"], "h9700f7e3g460eg41ecga42agef3fe8930f7a": ["| We are in agreement: A. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "87d910d1-81e6-6b2a-cf35-99f37fd48078"], "h5b90e446gd88cg486dgbd9fg15c95641a485": ["All right. Does anyone know how to open the damn thing?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "87d910d1-81e6-6b2a-cf35-99f37fd48078"], "h698fcf6eg206eg4efeg930fgb4cecc6259ca": ["Then let's return it. Virtue is not yet dead after all.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "c2173f32-52cc-a6ac-3bca-a16dbd9298de"], "h355d37dfg272fg4e0fgb5b8g193b61c6a43b": ["Very well. Let us waste no more words on the subject.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "c2173f32-52cc-a6ac-3bca-a16dbd9298de"], "h9d5c62eag649eg4b83ga10fg10841eebd573": ["What good souls we are, returning lost valuables.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "c2173f32-52cc-a6ac-3bca-a16dbd9298de"], "h5bfc3b59g814bg4b06gb9a1g949f0dccf09a": ["| We are in agreement: B. (Shadowheart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "c2173f32-52cc-a6ac-3bca-a16dbd9298de"], "ha92651cbgcbd1g4f3cga580g9ef0f866d8dd": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "c2173f32-52cc-a6ac-3bca-a16dbd9298de"], "ha3c18798g985ag448ag99f2g2537d26e0d29": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "c2173f32-52cc-a6ac-3bca-a16dbd9298de"], "h1c285189g647dg4a47gb730gb00cfd7ece26": ["| We are in agreement: B. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "c2173f32-52cc-a6ac-3bca-a16dbd9298de"], "h8ae069e5g99e8g4e89g8a1agc40298009cd7": ["| We are in agreement: B. (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "c2173f32-52cc-a6ac-3bca-a16dbd9298de"], "h42ff95e8gc553g42a2ga205gd0c001370325": ["Glad to hear we're not becoming a band of smugglers. We'll make sure it gets back to its owner.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "c2173f32-52cc-a6ac-3bca-a16dbd9298de"], "h170bfe85g42c6g44deg977cg2cb5321c213c": ["I say pry it open. A well-guarded chest contains only well-hidden mysteries.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "12251060-0b91-8741-7632-0d639977d246"], "h56a7afc9gdb59g4a85g9d08ga560a18527b2": ["No, open it. Weapons, armour - whatever's inside shall hurry our path to victory.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "12251060-0b91-8741-7632-0d639977d246"], "hc2b56fa5g630ag49d7g9f70g2f3a39462178": ["Come on, crack it open. I think we've earned it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "12251060-0b91-8741-7632-0d639977d246"], "h36848445g7d50g46aeg8cb3gcf7d40eeb37e": ["| I disagree. I want option A (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "12251060-0b91-8741-7632-0d639977d246"], "hdfa23278g7511g4c31g9e43g788b3bff5ec7": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "12251060-0b91-8741-7632-0d639977d246"], "h51bca9a1g518fg4845g9451g7d4efb6a19be": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "12251060-0b91-8741-7632-0d639977d246"], "h1ec5f2ffgfe2ag4968g9041g301166c19ea5": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "12251060-0b91-8741-7632-0d639977d246"], "hc3bb642fg335dg49f7g8a5dg3e527feb7bd4": ["| I disagree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "12251060-0b91-8741-7632-0d639977d246"], "hd1a1bb18g569dg4afeg9703g14abaf715398": ["I doubt the owner needs what's inside more than we do.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "12251060-0b91-8741-7632-0d639977d246"], "h8d2b9845gc5c9g4c44g8866g60ba3df7db05": ["We should return it to its owner, for certain. Have we not plundered enough?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "435d85c0-614f-b948-ff0b-f2d439d8f5f2"], "ha4bd956fg8782g4750g816cgf106eb6e0375": ["| I agree. I want option B (Laezel Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\PLA_PreciousCargo_RD.html", "435d85c0-614f-b948-ff0b-